title: Idaho SOS,  Presidential Primary results by county, Idaho, 2008
name: Idaho SOS,  Presidential Primary results by county, Idaho, 2008
description: The poly shapefile shows results of Idaho presidential primary results by county. It includes both Democratic and Republican candidates and percent votes received by each candidate. Note that in Idaho, one can vote for None of the Above in both the Democratic and Republican primaries.

author.source: Idaho Secretary of State Election Division
